data.description: Ranch living with huge upstairs bonus! This well-kept Southall home offers easy living, convenience, and a wonderful location. Relax in the spacious living room around the fireplace and soak up the natural sunlight through the windows. All first floor bedrooms make for simple one level living if preferred. Endless opportunities abound in the finished second level, perfect for entertaining, relaxing or secondary living. The pool table is already in place and waiting for you to rack ‘em up. Fire up some steaks on the grill and play catch in the backyard. All appliances to convey. Roof replaced in 2021, cooling unit in 2019. Southall is a wonderful, mature community with a swimming pool and tennis, boasting easy access to Downtown Raleigh, I-440 and area shopping and dining. Upstairs bonus space (746 square feet) and extra storage with low ceilings (157 square feet) are both non-permitted and finished by a prior owner.
